  "paragraphs": [
    {
      "para_id": "Q001362.1",
      "line_range": "1",
      "translation": "(1) To Enlil , king of all lands ."
    },
    {
      "para_id": "Q001362.3",
      "line_range": "3",
      "translation": "(3) When the gods commanded him , En-šakuš-ana , lord of Sumer , king of the Land , conquered Kiš , and captured Enbi-Eštar , king of Kiš . The leader of Akšak and the leader Kiš ... the city that he also did conquer ...."
    },
    {
      "para_id": "Q001362.20",
      "line_range": "20",
      "translation": "(1') He returned ... under their control , ( but ) he dedicated their statues , their precious metal and lapis lazuli , their timber and goods for Nibru to Enlil ."
    }
  ],
